{"tid":786306,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵閘機收費系統招標！要求支援 Apple Pay！","createTime":"2018-08-19T22:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T02:37:56.000Z","uid":66365,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e87720bb02e51c96d0c019e611af78b7fb07b4","tid":786306,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:50:17.000Z","msg":"早前，港鐵招標時只要求支援二維碼及八達通，被批明顯是為了支付寶／微信支付，沒有信用卡或 Apple Pay 支援，不過看來有轉機了！<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報報導指港鐵招標文件發現，上月推出更換閘機及售票機，成本預計 3 億，文件更求除了要支援八達通及二維碼外，更首次加入信用卡、Apple Pay 等支付方式。<br />\n<br />\n文件提到，先有 1500 台入閘機、420 台售票機會被取代，500 台入閘機會升級。而入閘機首次加入手機支付以及非接觸式 EMV 卡支援，那是未來用 Apple Pay、Google Pay、Paywave 等方式支付也沒有問題，免增值的煩惱。<br />\n<br />\n終於黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4354e14beea3c47f24eeaedf305ba1b53d87a7c3","tid":786306,"uid":32549,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:54:14.000Z","msg":"入閘時間增一倍"},{"pid":"81bd90e2ff4dde15c43fb78f80b98e7a46b592f8","tid":786306,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:59:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11f412f7b0c4573ed984bbe12230709abab59f27","tid":786306,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T23:00:10.000Z","msg":"睇左做超標"},{"pid":"71e0df28fb8e53b70efd05637273956662f1109f","tid":786306,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T23:16:31.000Z","msg":"張單水蛇春咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efcf975f4f874d6c35e7f59f1c7b4ef37652e2e","tid":786306,"uid":51747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T23:21:39.000Z","msg":"小動作嚟啫<br />\n根本最好就係放得張八達通入applepay同googlepay<br />\n你吹話八達通公司你管唔到，你未整多張交通卡出嚟囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家繁忙時間啲人用都會票慢少少都好明顯，仲想直接拍信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},